name: @looker/wholly-artifact
description: Looker Artifact API as a Table SDK
author: Looker

scripts.watch: yarn lerna exec --scope @looker/wholly-artifact --stream 'BABEL_ENV=build babel src --root-mode upward --out-dir lib/esm --source-maps --extensions .ts,.tsx --no-comments --watch'
scripts.watch:cjs: yarn lerna exec --scope @looker/wholly-artifact --stream 'BABEL_ENV=build_cjs babel src --root-mode upward --out-dir lib --source-maps --extensions .ts,.tsx --no-comments --watch'
